data.description: Check out this renovated open floor plan 3 bedroom / 2 bath home nestled in the heart of Asbury on a spacious .80-acre lot. This residence boasts a 24x40 detached building/shop for versatile use and perfect for the man of the house. Property also features a convenient detached carport. Embrace the tranquility of this property, offering both comfort and plenty of storage room. Metal roof - 2016 New SS appliances  Buffet and kitchen island to convey.
